{
  "texts": [
    "Topic 1 consists of publications that focussed on the development/application of novel TM algorithms in various domain.",
    "Literature reviewed (in Topic 1) indicates LDA is a popular TM algorithm and there are several extensions of LDA algorithm that have been proposed.",
    "For example, correlated topic model (Lafferty et al. 2005) was proposed to understand the correlation between topics via the logistic normal distribution and dynamic topic model (Blei and Lafferty 2006) was developed to model the time evolution of topics in a document.",
    "Other notable LDA variants are hierarchical Dirichlet process (Teh et al. 2004), supervised LDA (Mcauliffe and Blei 2007), FastLDA (Porteous et al. 2008), relational topic model (Chang and Blei, 2009) (Korshunova et al. 2019).",
    "Prior studies criticised LDA that the model struggles with short text and thus, Bi-term topic model (Yan et al. 2013) was proposed to solve the problem of short text."
  ]
}